---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" description="Disclaimer — AI usage, editorial standards, and feedback for The Humanitarian Commons.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          This website was constructed with help from AI. The model used was Claude Cowork,
          mostly using Opus 4.6 model.
        </p>

        <h2>What the AI helped with</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Construct the code for the site and help with the technical web design, development, and hosting.</li>
          <li>Scheduled push of contents to the site.</li>
          <li>Debugging and ensuring that the site functions as intended.</li>
          <li>Fact check all the content of the site against publicly available records.</li>
          <li>Scanning for documents, updates, and literature search. Every piece of content was then human-read and verified to avoid any fabricated or hallucinated content and to ensure relevance and accuracy.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What the AI was not used for</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>The design of the structure of the site.</li>
          <li>The compilation of the content of the site.</li>
          <li>The writing of the content of the site.</li>
          <li>The linking of content.</li>
          <li>Editorial judgement on what to include or exclude.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          This project is run privately and individually and is not for profit. The use of AI is
          minimised to guarantee efficiency but is conscious of the risks of AI usage for the
          accuracy of information as well as the environmental and labour costs of AI, especially
          in the Global South and in contexts relevant to humanitarianism. This balance is
          revisited regularly and adjusted as appropriate.
        </p>

        <h2>Feedback</h2>
        <p>
          For any feedback, suggestions, or corrections you can leave comments
          <a href="https://forms.gle/u1KqJF1BSiD56VZu5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .prose {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .prose h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
</style>
